<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">使用屏幕键盘</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">如果计算机上没有连接键盘或不喜欢使用键盘，您可以打开<span class="em">屏幕键盘</span>来输入文字。</p>
<div class="note" title="备注">
<svg width="24" height="24" version="1.1">
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m4 3h16c0.554 0 1 0.446 1 1v11h-6v6h-11c-0.554 0-1-0.446-1-1v-16c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">如果您使用触摸屏，屏幕键盘将自动启用</p></div></div></div>
</div>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">打开<span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.zh-CN#activities" title="活动概览">活动</a></span>概览后输入<span class="gui">辅助功能</span>。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">点击<span class="gui">辅助功能</span>打开面板。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">选择 <span class="gui">打字</span> 部分将其打开。</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">切换 <span class="gui">屏幕键盘</span> 开关为开启状态。</p></li>
</ol></div></div></div>
<p class="p">当您下次打字时，屏幕键盘将从屏幕底部打开。</p>
<p class="p">按 <span class="gui">?123</span> 按钮进入数字和符号输入。再按 <span class="gui">=/&lt;</span> 按钮可输入更多符号。要返回字母键盘，请按 <span class="gui">ABC</span> 按钮。</p>
<p class="p">您可以按<span class="gui"><span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/go-down-symbolic.svg" height="16" width="16" class="media media-inline" alt="向下"></span></span></span>按钮来暂时隐藏键盘。当下次点进能用键盘的地方时，它会自动重新显示。在触摸屏上，您也可以通过<span class="link"><a href="touchscreen-gestures.html.zh-CN" title="使用触摸板和触摸屏手势">从底部边缘向上拖动</a></span>来呼出屏幕键盘。</p>
<p class="p">按 <span class="gui"><span class="media"><span class="media media-image"><img src="figures/emoji-flags-symbolic.svg" height="16" width="16" class="media media-inline" alt="旗帜"></span></span></span>按钮来更改<span class="link"><a href="session-language.html.zh-CN" title="更改系统语言">语言</a></span>或<span class="link"><a href="keyboard-layouts.html.zh-CN" title="使用其他键盘布局">输入源</a></span>的设置。</p>
</div>
